data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 3-bed, 2-bath 1930 sqft gem has undergone a number of upgrades and interior remodels over the last few years. Bask in the beauty of your lake view from the spacious front patio, perfect for morning coffees or evening cocktails. The solar panels, owned free and clear, bring eco-friendly living to new heights, with total 12 month electric charges coming in under $300.  THAT'S NOT ONLY JULY!!!  THAT'S THE WHOLE 12 MONTHS COMBINED!!!   Plus a hybrid water heater and double pane windows make this an energy-efficient haven that can be yours.  Act fast and embrace a lifestyle of comfort and sustainability!
